# Burp Suite - HTTP Interception  
Burp Suite is a web security testing tool used for intercepting, modifying, and analyzing HTTP requests.  

## ðŸ”¹ How I Used Burp Suite  
- Configured *intercept mode* to analyze login traffic  
- Captured *plaintext login credentials* being sent via HTTP  

## ðŸ”¹ Useful Burp Suite Features  
- *Proxy Tab:* Intercept and modify HTTP requests  
- *Repeater Tab:* Manually send and analyze requests  
- *Intruder Tab:* Automate brute force attacks  

